[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1104] updated Mamba/Conda info parsing and fixed syntax errors
.
Kissaki made many improvements:
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1103] Updated some fish-sourced generated completion files
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1102] Updated more fish-sourced generated completion files
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1101] Dropped the generated 
``highlight.nu``
 file
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1098] Dropped added PATHs on folder leave
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1097] Used 
``path join``
 to join path parts
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1096] Supported configs with no hooks in 
``rusty-paths.nu``
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1094] Fixed 
``parse-fish.nu``
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1093] Improved the auto-generated 
``README.md``
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1092] Removed duplicate "moved" auto-generated files from the old location
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1091] Fixed 
``winget show``
 completions
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1090] Fixed 
``winget``
 completions breaking 
``winget show``
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1089] Added 
``md-to-clip``
 custom completions
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1088] Dropped a draft note
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1087] Improved git completions
.
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1086] Ported 
``parse_aws_s3_ls.nu``
 from before v0.60
.
kiil 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1100] added a games folder with a simple game demonstrating Nu code concepts
.
jaredmontoya 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nu_scripts/pull/1099] added a 
``capture-foreign-env``
 module
.
